Every weekday, Robert Marawa hosts his award-winning sports show, Marawa Sports Worldwide, right here on SowetanLIVE. The 90-minute show is streamed live on our website every Monday to Friday from 5.30pm, and on Vuma FM in Durban and Rise FM in Mbombela. In a Marawa Sports Worldwide exclusive this month, Marawa spoke to one of SA's most celebrated football players and coaches. AmaZulu coach Benni McCarthy discussed his team's CAF Champions League match against Horoya; his move to KwaZulu-Natal; the incredible football spirit at AmaZulu; and the team's prospects for the rest of the season.